Amesta Living - A Sanctuary In The City

Info Detail

Amesta Living is a modern oasis that provides a healthier and happier quality of life for your beloved family. The development of a 60-hectare integrated area is the ideal option for people in East Surabaya's different property needs.

Innovative Residential Supports Productivity

Bringing harmony and balance to life by carrying the concept of the green environment and sustainable development. Presenting houses that rely on natural lighting and air circulation to provide comfort and freshness, thereby stimulating residents’ productivity.

Japandi’s Design

Each house is created with a Japandi’s Design  (Japanese – Scandinavian) idea based on a modern-simple and current lifestyle that maximizes the function of each room, still remaining warm and comforting on the inside.

Strategic Location in East Surabaya

Located in East Surabaya, precisely Zero kilometers from OERR (Outer East Ring Road), close to the airport, Juanda ring road, and educational areas, Amesta Living is equipped with a variety of the best facilities ranging from SOHO, retail, commercial, and lifestyle malls.

A Peaceful and Healthy Environment

The development of an integrated area that prioritizes the concept of harmony values in order to bring humans and nature closer together. Amesta Living has a Community Center that serves as a shared social space with a variety of supporting facilities for resident interaction and social events.

Management of The Environment

Amesta Living is managed professionally by entrusting Provest as an estate management firm. This service provides added value and convenience in environmental and estate management, as well as helping residents to obtain various other services they need.

Environmental Facilities

The concept of developing an integrated area presents the convenience and comfort of living with the presence of a commercial area, jogging track, children’s playground, and water promenade facilities.

Clean Environment

A clean and tidy environment and a professional management system are priorities.

Best Accessibility

Greater access to various strategic locations such as Juanda International Airport, access to the toll roads of Sidoarjo, Surabaya, and Mojokerto, as well as proximity to educational centers and other facilities such as commercial centers and hospitals.

Rapid Development of the Region

Being part of the East Surabaya area development program which is running very massively in line with the development of public infrastructure. This development increases the value of the Amesta Living area in the long term.

Water Promenade

An open area of 8,500 m2 becomes an oasis for anyone who is present in this area. This open area is the most important social facility for residents as a community center equipped with water features and a water promenade that beautify the environmental landscape.

Facilities

Community Center

Located in an area of 2,000 m2. This area is prepared as a collaboration area between residents to interact, socialize, or just enjoy time with family, relatives, and neighbors.

SOHO & Commercial Area

To meet the needs of its residents, there are a variety of commercial facilities for SOHO, cafes, restaurants, and retail that are easily accessible on walking distance.

Playground and Sports

The importance of a healthy lifestyle and safety for children in playing around the house is a priority. Amesta Living provides a comfortable playground area and jogging track.

Integrated Security System

Comfort and safety are Amesta Living’s priorities. This area is professionally managed with a variety of integrated security system services to provide a sense of peace for its citizens.
